Terms of Service!
1. Be Respectful
Be respectful toward others whether they are staff members or not. Have civil conversations and does not argue. Arguing may start a drama that can involve more people.

2. No Direct swearing is highly discouraged
Do not directly swear at someone. Minor swearing is allowed but any disparaging language towards any individual is prohibited. We follow a zero-tolerance policy towards toxicity.

3. No Politics
Politics aren't allowed on gibbon business.

4. No Mini-Modding
Let the staff members take care of that. Getting involved could lead to you getting punished. Try to stay out of it.
